'''Richard J. Wood''' is a mathematics [[professor]] at [[Dalhousie University]] in [[Halifax Regional Municipality|Halifax]], [[Nova Scotia]], [[Canada]]. He graduated from [[McMaster University]] in 1972 with his [[M.Sc.]] and then later went on to do his [[Ph.D.]] at Dalhousie University. He is interested in [[category theory]] and [[Lattice (order)|lattice theory]].<ref name="urlWood">{{cite web |url=http://www.mscs.dal.ca/Faculty/rjwood.html |title=Wood, Richard |work= |accessdate=2009-01-25}}</ref>

